    <field id="description" text-type="text/html"><![CDATA[For our question item we need some extra fields which should be created during this exercise. We need an answer field, an enumeration to slect a topic this question is about and we also want to use our custom priority to define how urgent a question is. In addition the selected priority should be dependant on the topic we choose.<br/>
 
<ul>
  <li>Before we create our custom fields we shoukd create our enumeration values which can be selected by these custom fields.<br/>
    Open <span style="font-style: italic;">Administration&gt;Work Items&gt;Enumerations</span> to create the enumerations<br/>
    <img src="attachment:newenum.jpg" style="width: 600px;height: 188px;"/> </li>
  <ul>
    <li>Select question as workitem type and add following enumeration values<br/>
      <img src="attachment:52-screenshot-20141029-063653.png" style="width: 246px;height: 150px;"/><br/>
      </li>
    <ul>
      <li>topicenum (enumeration values: process, configuration, trainingMaterials, polarion, other)<br/>
        <img src="attachment:53-screenshot-20141029-063654.png" style="width: 704px;height: 133px;"/></li>
      <li>prio (enumeration values: urgent, notUrgent, average)</li>
    </ul>
  </ul>
  <li>Open <span style="font-style: italic;">Administration&gt;Work Items&gt;Custom Fields</span> to define the custom fields</li>
  <ul>
    <li>Create a new question-custom-fields.xml</li>
    <li>Add folowing custom fields</li>
    <ul>
      <li>answer: (type:rich text)</li>
      <li>topic: (enumeration value: topicenum)<br/>
        </li>
      <li>customPriority: (enumeration value: prio)</li>
      <li>customPriority should be dependant on a selected topic</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Click  <img src="attachment:54-screenshot-20141029-063654.png" style="width: 30px;height: 20px;"/>to add a dependency</li>
        <li>Select Topic as field and add a mapping</li>
        <ul>
          <li>Questions regarding Training Materials should not be Urgent. All other topics should select all custom Priorities.<br/>
            <img src="attachment:56-screenshot-20141029-063744.png" style="width: 654px;height: 381px;"/></li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <li>Verify if you create a new question and select Training Materials as topic you can only select Average or Not Urgent</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
 <br/>]]></field>
